QuestData.Title: Invasion
QuestData.Description: <A long knife with a skull ornament on its hilt sticks out of the militiaman's ribs. As you look around for clues, you spot a pair of savage-looking warships at the shore.>$B$B<Gilneas is being invaded. Bring word back to Duskhaven's Mayor, Gwen Armstead.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Gwen Armstead in Duskhaven.
QuestData.RewardText: Forsaken! Quick, $n! We must mount a defense.
